name: SVBPours
description: A Collection of 22 Original Acrylic Pour Art Pieces I have done. Acrylic pouring is a painting technique where acrylic paint is mixed with some type of pouring medium and then poured onto a surface in a variety of ways. Sometimes colours are poured directly from individual cups, and other times multiple colours are combined into one cup and poured together. 16 of 22 in my collection.
